#: utils/analyzer.py:116
msgid "Your CV has an excellent structure that makes it easy to read."
msgstr "Rezyumengiz ajoyib tuzilishga ega, uni o'qish juda oson."

#: utils/analyzer.py:118
msgid ""
"The structure of your CV is good, but could be organized slightly better."
msgstr ""
"Rezyumengizning tuzilishi yaxshi, biroq biroz yaxshiroq tashkil etilishi "
"mumkin."

#: utils/analyzer.py:119
msgid "- Consider moving your most relevant experience closer to the top."
msgstr "- Eng tegishli tajribangizni yuqoriroqqa ko'chirishni ko'rib chiqing."

#: utils/analyzer.py:121
msgid ""
"The CV structure is somewhat confusing and may be hard for recruiters to "
"scan."
msgstr ""
"Rezyume tuzilishi biroz chalkash va ish beruvchilar ko'zdan kechirishi uchun"
" qiyin bo'lishi mumkin."

#: utils/analyzer.py:122
msgid "- Use clear headings (Experience, Education, Skills)."
msgstr "- Aniq sarlavhalardan foydalaning (Tajriba, Ta'lim, Ko'nikmalar)."

#: utils/analyzer.py:123
msgid "- Ensure chronological order is used correctly."
msgstr "- Xronologik tartibdan to'g'ri foydalanilganiga ishonch hosil qiling."

#: utils/analyzer.py:127
msgid "You have a strong, well-defined skills section."
msgstr "Sizda kuchli, yaxshi ta'riflangan ko'nikmalar bo'limi bor."

#: utils/analyzer.py:129
msgid "Your skills section is decent, but could be more targeted."
msgstr ""
"Sizning ko'nikmalar bo'limingiz yaxshi, biroq ko'proq maqsadli bo'lishi "
"mumkin."

#: utils/analyzer.py:130
msgid "- Add more specific technical keywords related to your industry."
msgstr "- Sanoatingizga tegishli aniqroq texnik kalit so'zlarni qo'shing."

#: utils/analyzer.py:132
msgid ""
"The skills section is lacking depth and might not pass Applicant Tracking "
"Systems (ATS)."
msgstr ""
"Ko'nikmalar bo'limida chuqurlik yetishmaydi va Nomzodlarni Kuzatish "
"Tizimlaridan (ATS) o'ta olmasligi mumkin."

#: utils/analyzer.py:133
msgid "- Create a dedicated 'Skills' section."
msgstr "- Maxsus 'Ko'nikmalar' bo'limini yarating."

#: utils/analyzer.py:134
msgid "- List both hard and soft skills clearly."
msgstr "- Qattiq va yumshoq ko'nikmalarni aniq sanab o'ting."

#: utils/analyzer.py:138
msgid "Your descriptions are impactful and action-oriented."
msgstr "Tavsiflaringiz ta'sirli va harakatga yo'naltirilgan."

#: utils/analyzer.py:140
msgid "Your experience descriptions are okay, but lack measurable impact."
msgstr "Tajriba tavsiflaringiz yaxshi, ammo o'lchanadigan ta'sirga ega emas."

#: utils/analyzer.py:141
msgid "- Add quantifiable achievements (e.g., 'Increased sales by 20%')."
msgstr ""
"- Miqdoriy yutuqlarni qo'shing (masalan, 'Sotuvlarni 20% ga oshirdi')."

#: utils/analyzer.py:143
msgid "The content focuses too much on daily duties rather than achievements."
msgstr "Tarkib yutuqlardan ko'ra ko'proq kundalik vazifalarga qaratilgan."

#: utils/analyzer.py:144
msgid "- Use strong action verbs (Led, Developed, Managed)."
msgstr ""
"- Kuchli harakat fe'llaridan foydalaning (Boshqargan, Rivojlantirgan, "
"Boshqargan)."

#: utils/analyzer.py:145
msgid ""
"- Focus on what you accomplished, not just what you were assigned to do."
msgstr ""
"- Faqat sizga yuklatilgan vazifalarga emas, balki erishgan natijalaringizga "
"e'tibor qarating."

#: utils/analyzer.py:148
msgid "Recommended Job Positions:"
msgstr "Tavsiya Etilgan Ish O'rinlari:"

